cultural capital of the world.\", \"from\": 6389, \"to\": 6445, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many ways\", \"from\": 6400, \"to\": 6409}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 6435, \"to\": 6444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are going to see a lot of star power, a lot of excitement, a lot of energy, and a place that is truly diverse and brings the world together.\\\"\", \"from\": 6446, \"to\": 6591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 6467, \"to\": 6472}, {\"ngram\": \"star power\", \"from\": 6476, \"to\": 6486}, {\"ngram\": \"excitement\", \"from\": 6497, \"to\": 6507}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 6509, \"to\": 6514}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 6518, \"to\": 6524}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 6530, \"to\": 6537}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 6571, \"to\": 6580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wasserman to Tirico on LA28's venues: \\\"We start with what is the most remarkable stadium in football [SoFi Stadium], where we will have the Parade of Nations and Opening Ceremony as well as swimming.\", \"from\": 6593, \"to\": 6792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6755, \"end\": 6771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9999999999336069, \"rank\": 6.641999006409599e-11, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tirico\", \"from\": 6606, \"to\": 6612}, {\"ngram\": \"LA28's venues\", \"from\": 6616, \"to\": 6629}, {\"ngram\": \"the most remarkable stadium\", \"from\": 6654, \"to\": 6681}, {\"ngram\": \"football\", \"from\": 6685, \"to\": 6693}, {\"ngram\": \"[SoFi Stadium\", \"from\": 6694, \"to\": 6707}, {\"ngram\": \"the Parade\", \"from\": 6729, \"to\": 6739}, {\"ngram\": \"Nations\", \"from\": 6743, \"to\": 6750}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We go back to the Coliseum, the first venue ever to host three Oly