"from\": 7773, \"to\": 7802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every backdrop, arresting.\", \"from\": 7805, \"to\": 7831, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every backdrop\", \"from\": 7805, \"to\": 7819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then from there, on to Milan-Cortina for the next Winter Games.\", \"from\": 7832, \"to\": 7899, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Milan-Cortina\", \"from\": 7859, \"to\": 7872}, {\"ngram\": \"the next Winter Games\", \"from\": 7877, \"to\": 7898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It looked to me, and it's turning out this way, like a chance for the Olympics to get its groove back.\", \"from\": 7900, \"to\": 8002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 7953, \"to\": 7961}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 7966, \"to\": 7978}, {\"ngram\": \"its groove\", \"from\": 7986, \"to\": 7996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From an American perspective, you come to Los Angeles in '28, this is the time - obviously viewing habits have changed, the way people feel about sports may have changed - but this is the time for the Olympics to get its groove back, and it's turning out that way.\\\"\", \"from\": 8003, \"to\": 8268, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8011, \"end\": 8019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9988762136089714, \"rank\": 0.001125050646924626, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 8045, \"end\": 8056, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.559383923660274e-23, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 8073, \"to\": 8081}, {\"ngram\": \"obviously viewing habits\", \"from\": 8084, \"to\": 8108}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 8123, \"to\": 8130}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 8131, \"to\": 8137}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 8149, \"to\": 8155}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 8187, \"to\": 8195}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 8200, \"to\": 8212}, {\"ngram\": \"its groove\", \"from\": 8220, \"to\": 8230}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Al Michaels on the 1980 Lake Placid Olympics: \\\"The country needed something to galvanize it, to make us feel more united, and only at an Olympic Games can something like that happen.\\\"\", \"from\": 8270, \"to\": 8453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8270, \"end\": 8281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Michaels\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7515121246051953e-52, \"text\": \"Al Michaels\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Michaels\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Michaels\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 1980 Lake Placid Olympics\", \"from\": 8285, \"to\": 8314}, {\"ngram\": \"The country\", \"from\": 8317, \"to\": 8328}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 8336, \"to\": 8345}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 8371, \"to\": 8373}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Games\", \"from\": 8404, \"to\": 8420}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 8425, \"to\": 8434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Michaels on the Olympic Games in general: \\\"It's the one time when everybody kind of gets together.\", \"from\": 8455, \"to\": 8553, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 8467, \"to\": 8484}, {\"ngram\": \"the one time\", \"from\": 8503, \"to\": 8515}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 8521, \"to\": 8530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The world comes to one place\\u2026 it's a feel-good thing.\", \"from\": 8554, \"to\": 8607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The world\", \"from\": 8554, \"to\": 8563}, {\"ngram\": \"one place\", \"from\": 8573, \"to\": 8582